WEBVTT

00:02.041 --> 00:03.734
<i>Previously on "The Outpost"...</i>

00:03.737 --> 00:05.094
- GARRET: What are they doing?
- TALON: Checking ears.

00:05.096 --> 00:06.812
- Why ears?
- They're looking for me.

00:06.814 --> 00:09.113
I'm just a sword. A cold piece of steel

00:09.116 --> 00:11.382
- in the hands of Everit Dred.
- [SCREAMS]

00:11.385 --> 00:13.852
- You're good, Blackblood.
- Better than you.

00:13.854 --> 00:15.039
Marshal Wythers!

00:15.042 --> 00:16.274
Why are you in here?

00:16.277 --> 00:18.177
[SCREAMS]

00:20.757 --> 00:23.525
Gallows Rock. Sundown before dark moon.

00:23.528 --> 00:25.151
The smith said I need
to find the Book of Names

00:25.153 --> 00:27.179
before something called
the Dragman finds me.

00:27.182 --> 00:29.600
I kind of need a little,
small favor in return.

00:29.602 --> 00:32.537
- What kind of favor?
- I'm going traveling to deliver some stuff,

00:32.539 --> 00:34.806
and I need a travel companion.

00:34.808 --> 00:36.240
Will you come with me?

00:36.243 --> 00:38.207
People find out about
you and who you are,

00:38.210 --> 00:40.109
men will flock to your banners.

00:40.112 --> 00:41.695
GRUFF MAN: Hail to the queen!

00:41.778 --> 00:43.554
ALL: Hail to the queen!

00:43.625 --> 00:45.757
Hail to the queen!

00:47.000 --> 00:53.074
